e, quark is a soft cheese popular in Northern and Eastern Europe. Quark can also be purchased in some delis and speciality food stores.","To save time, make quark and berry sauce ahead of time.","Use fresh berries instead of frozen when in season.","This recipe is a source of both calcium and protein."],"basicInfo":["medium","35m","3h 35m","12 portions"]}